<H3> <TI>   Trieste Citizens: Change of Treaty Osimo `Impractical' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Trieste Citizens: Change of Treaty Osimo `Impractical' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR1705125894 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1027 GMT 17 
May 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR1705125894 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome ANSAMAIL Database </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


