<F P=101> Switzerland </F>
<H3> <TI>   Council Chairman Discusses UN Contingent </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Council Chairman Discusses UN Contingent </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR1805102394 Bern ATSA/SDAA Database in French 0541 GMT 18 
May 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR1805102394 </F>
<F P=104>  Bern ATSA/SDAA Database </F>
<F P=105>  French </F>


<TEXT>
