  Daskalov on Friday also said that his country was paying a 
heavy price as a result of the UN trade embargo against the 
rump-Yugoslavia -- Serbia and Montenegro -- for the Serbs' role 
in the wars in Bosnia-Herzegovina and Croatia. 

