  [Excerpt] President Glavkos Kliridhis met British Deputy 
Foreign Secretary Tom Richardson in the Presidential Palace this 
morning. Speaking afterward, Richardson said the current 
process in the Cyprus issue has reached a decisive point. He 
expressed the hope that there would be an agreement on the 
confidence-building measures before the UN secretary general 
submits his report to the Security Council. After the report is 
