exportation. 
  Ciller said exportation is extremely important nowadays and 
this credit that we have transferred to Eximbank is a good 
opportunity for our industry to continue its production toward 
exportation. 
  Ciller said `We have allocated this money from public 
sector's resources'. 
  She said the difficulties have not finished yet but Turkey 
is 
resolved to overcome all its problems step by step. 

