<H3> <TI>   Herzog Wins Presidency in Third Ballot </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Herzog Wins Presidency in Third Ballot </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2305162694 Berlin N-TV in German 1618 GMT 23 May 94 </F>
