<F P=105>  German </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Summary] The third ballot for the German presidency was 
won by Roman Herzog with 696 votes. Johannes Rau received 605 
votes, and the Republican candidate Hans Hirzel won 11 votes. 

</TEXT>

