<H3> <TI>   Scharping Demands More EU Funds for Germany </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Scharping Demands More EU Funds for Germany </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2105185994 Hamburg DPA in German 1714 GMT 21 May 94--FOR 
