<H4>    Meets Cetin, Karayalcin </H4>

<F P=102> TA1705190194 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1700 
GMT 16 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1705190194 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


