<H3> <TI>   Security Forces Continue Operations Against PKK </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Security Forces Continue Operations Against PKK </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    15 `Terrorists' Die in Agri </H4>

<F P=102> TA2005103894 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1000 
GMT 20 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2005103894 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report] </F>
  [Text] Fifteen terrorists belonging to the PKK [Workers 
Party of Kurdistan] terrorist organization have been killed in 
clashes with the security forces in Agri's Tendurek Mountains. 
According to information obtained by a Turkish Radio and 
Television correspondent, many weapons and large amounts of 
ammunition have been seized in the area. The operation 
continues. 
  Four persons were killed when a private car hit a mine laid 
by terrorists near the Topluca village of Mardin's Savur 
District. 

</TEXT>

