<F P=100> SPAIN </F>
<H3> <TI>   Defense Minister Sees Russian Role in Partnership </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Defense Minister Sees Russian Role in Partnership </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2505191194 Madrid RNE International in Spanish 1300 GMT 25 
