  [Begin Hernandez recording] [passage omitted] According to 
Spanish Defense Minister Julian Garcia Vargas, Moscow's 
initiative would be appropriate for the Partnership for Peace 
put forward by NATO. 
  [Vargas] I think it does have its place. If you take into 
consideration what we were saying yesterday--and what is common 
knowledge relayed by all the media--that France.... [pauses] 
excuse me, that Russia is a superpower, naturally it seems good 
